T16TD4416E:350a-3: dkon mchog gsum gyi bde legs kyi tshigs su bcad pa /
T16TD4416E:350a-4: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16TD4416E:350a-5: sangs rgyas gtso la yon tan mchog mnga' pa //
T16TD4416E:350a-6: che dgus mchod cing smon lam sprin tshogs 'dus //
T16TD4416E:350b-0: go 'phang mchog @350b brnyes bstod pa'i char 'bab pa'i //
T16TD4416E:350b-1: bkra shis dam pa deng 'dir bde legs shog / skyob pa'i chos la legs pa'i tshogs mnga' ba //
T16TD4416E:350b-2: shin tu phan pa bde ba nges gsungs pa //
T16TD4416E:350b-3: 'khor ba rtag bde mya nang med thob pa'i //
T16TD4416E:350b-4: bkra shis dam pa deng 'dir bde legs shog / dge 'dun che la mthu dpal rmad mnga' ba //
T16TD4416E:350b-5: bslab gzhi legs bcas brtson pa'i sbyor ba can //
T16TD4416E:350b-6: bdag gzhan don che sgrub pa'i lam zhugs pa'i //
T16TD4416E:350b-7: bkra shis dam pa deng 'dri bde legs shog //
T16TD4416E:350b-8: dkon mchog gsum gyi bde legs kyi tshigs su bcad pa rdzogs so /
